name: Southern All Stars: Space MOSA Space Museum of Southern Art
overview: Southern All Stars: Space MOSA "Space Museum of Southern Art is a database of the Southern All Stars group showing pictures, lyrics and songs of the group and also some live videos and video clip medley of the 43 singles. The software is divided into 3 different discs. Disc 1 is the museum, Disc 2 is the Library and Disc 3 is the theater.
